نُذِقۡهُ عَذَابٗا كَبِيرٗا </div><div>٩١</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>وَمَآ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> أَرۡسَلۡنَا قَبۡلَكَ مِنَ ٱلۡمُرۡسَلِينَ إِلَّآ إِنَّهُمۡ </div><div>لَيَأۡكُلُونَ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>ٱلطَّعَامَ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> وَيَمۡشُونَ فِي ٱلۡأَسۡوَاقِۗ وَجَعَلۡنَا </div><div>بَعۡضَكُمۡ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>لِبَعۡضٖ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> <a data-content='ابتلاء ومحنة' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>فِتۡنَةً</a> أَتَصۡبِرُونَۗ وَكَانَ رَبُّكَ بَصِيرٗا </div><div>٠٢</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'></div>",
